name: Blog App UI KIT (Community)
description: Hello Everyone. Today we are presenting our new app called Confect - Blog Reading App. It is an online journal where people can share their experiences or share information with other readers on any topic. This app will allow you to read any kind of blog from professionals. Also, you can make your profile and post any kind of blog. In this app, you will get 80+ app screens with Dark UI. Its fully customizable, easy to change colors. Download and enjoy the app. Available in Figma, XD & Sketch
